                <h1 class="article__title">Raphinha named best LaLiga player in 2024/25</h1>

                <div class="article__summary">Brazilian forward key to FC Barcelona title win, contributing 18 goals and 11 assists</div>

                <div class="article__meta">
                    


                    <div class="article__publisher">
                        <div class="article__author">fcbarcelona.com</div>
