                <div class="article__body">

                    <div class="article__content js-article-body js-text-share-body"><p>Another LaLiga award for the blaugranes. After <a href="https://www.fcbarcelona.com/en/noticias/4277069/hansi-flick-designado-mejor-entrenador-de-la-liga" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hansi Flick was named as coach of the season</a> and <a href="https://www.fcbarcelona.com/en/futbol/primer-equipo/noticias/4278746/lamine-yamal-mejor-jugador-sub-23" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Lamine Yamal was named as best U23 player</a>, it's now time for <strong>Raphinha</strong> to receive the accolades, as the Brazilian has been named as best LaLiga player after an outstanding 2024/25 season.</p>
<p>Flick's arrival as coach coincided with the Brazilian taking his football to another level, becoming a very attack-minded player and a real difference-maker for Barça. So much so that he has been recognised as the standout player in LaLiga of the season just ended.</p><div class="articleWidget center">

    <section class="static-promo  ">

    <a href="https://store.fcbarcelona.com/collections/new-kit?ext=OCM_25-26&utm_source=WebBarca&utm_medium=Article&utm_campaign=NewKit2526_EN_BLM_KITS_WW&utm_term=NewKit2526" class="thumbnail thumbnail--wide thumbnail--promo-wide thumbnail--promo-link  "  >
<figure class="thumbnail__figure">
    <div class="thumbnail__picture-wrapper">
        <div class="thumbnail__picture">
            <svg class="thumbnail__default" >
                <use xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:href="/resources/v3.4.5-7905/i/svg-output/club-badges.svg#BCN"></use>
            </svg>
            <span class="visually-hidden">label.aria.barcelonabadge</span>
                        <picture class="lazy-image js-lazy-picture thumbnail__picture-element lazy-load" data-img-alt="Llanament1aEquipaci1stKit1rEquip20252026_nilventura_fcbarcelona (2)"  data-odir="true" data-img-src="https://www.fcbarcelona.com/photo-resources/2025/07/15/7cd39435-4ba2-48af-b90f-642f2ab74c6f/Llanament1aEquipaci1stKit1rEquip20252026_nilventura_fcbarcelona-2-.jpg">

                            <source srcset="" data-image-src="https://www.fcbarcelona.com/photo-resources/2025/07/15/7cd39435-4ba2-48af-b90f-642f2ab74c6f/Llanament1aEquipaci1stKit1rEquip20252026_nilventura_fcbarcelona-2-.jpg?width=312&height=184, https://www.fcbarcelona.com/photo-resources/2025/07/15/7cd39435-4ba2-48af-b90f-642f2ab74c6f/Llanament1aEquipaci1stKit1rEquip20252026_nilventura_fcbarcelona-2-.jpg?width=312&height=184?width=940&height=940 2x" media="(max-width: 320px)">

                            <source srcset="" data-image-src="https://www.fcbarcelona.com/photo-resources/2025/07/15/7cd39435-4ba2-48af-b90f-642f2ab74c6f/Llanament1aEquipaci1stKit1rEquip20252026_nilventura_fcbarcelona-2-.jpg?width=640&height=400, https://www.fcbarcelona.com/photo-resources/2025/07/15/7cd39435-4ba2-48af-b90f-642f2ab74c6f/Llanament1aEquipaci1stKit1rEquip20252026_nilventura_fcbarcelona-2-.jpg?width=1280&height=800 2x" media="(max-width: 840px)">

                            <source srcset="" data-image-src="https://www.fcbarcelona.com/photo-resources/2025/07/15/7cd39435-4ba2-48af-b90f-642f2ab74c6f/Llanament1aEquipaci1stKit1rEquip20252026_nilventura_fcbarcelona-2-.jpg?width=312&height=184, https://www.fcbarcelona.com/photo-resources/2025/07/15/7cd39435-4ba2-48af-b90f-642f2ab74c6f/Llanament1aEquipaci1stKit1rEquip20252026_nilventura_fcbarcelona-2-.jpg?width=312&height=184?width=940&height=940 2x">

                            <img src="" data-image-src="https://www.fcbarcelona.com/photo-resources/2025/07/15/7cd39435-4ba2-48af-b90f-642f2ab74c6f/Llanament1aEquipaci1stKit1rEquip20252026_nilventura_fcbarcelona-2-.jpg?width=312&height=184" alt="Llanament1aEquipaci1stKit1rEquip20252026_nilventura_fcbarcelona (2)" class="thumbnail__image"/>
                        </picture>
        </div>
    </div>

    <figcaption class="thumbnail__caption">
        <div class="thumbnail__text">
            <div class="thumbnail__title">Want Raphinha's jersey?</div>
                <div class="thumbnail__desc">Get the Brazilian's shirt</div>
        </div>
            <div class="static-promo__link">
                BUY IT!
                <svg class="static-promo__link-icon"><use xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:href="/resources/v3.4.5-7905/i/svg-output/icn.svg#arrow-right"></use></svg>
                <span class="visually-hidden">label.aria.clock</span>
            </div>
    </figcaption>
</figure>

    </a>

    </section>
</div><h2>An amazing year</h2>
<p>Raphinha has really stepped up and you only have to look at the numbers for proof. His first season in the domestic competition was 2022/23 when he scored seven goals in blaugrana, while last season he scored six. This season he has tripled that number, scoring <strong>18 goals in 36 LaLiga games</strong>. A true reflection of his attacking importance for Barça throughout the campaign.</p><div class="articleWidget center">


    <div class="embeddable-photo" data-observe="embeddable-photo" data-portrait="false">

        <div class="embeddable-photo__container">
            <picture class="embeddable-photo__picture ">
                    <source media="(max-width: 688px)" srcset="https://www.fcbarcelona.com/photo-resources/2024/10/28/f9613f00-b7bd-4087-a579-02a4ed507b03/mini__GP11513.jpg?width=640&height=400, https://www.fcbarcelona.com/photo-resources/2024/10/28/f9613f00-b7bd-4087-a579-02a4ed507b03/mini__GP11513.jpg?width=640&height=400 2x">
                    <source media="(max-width: 888px)" srcset="https://www.fcbarcelona.com/photo-resources/2024/10/28/f9613f00-b7bd-4087-a579-02a4ed507b03/mini__GP11513.jpg?width=840&height=525, https://www.fcbarcelona.com/photo-resources/2024/10/28/f9613f00-b7bd-4087-a579-02a4ed507b03/mini__GP11513.jpg?width=1680&height=1050 2x">
                <source srcset="https://www.fcbarcelona.com/photo-resources/2024/10/28/f9613f00-b7bd-4087-a579-02a4ed507b03/mini__GP11513.jpg?width=1200&height=750, https://www.fcbarcelona.com/photo-resources/2024/10/28/f9613f00-b7bd-4087-a579-02a4ed507b03/mini__GP11513.jpg?width=2400&height=1500 2x">

                <img src="https://www.fcbarcelona.com/photo-resources/2024/10/28/f9613f00-b7bd-4087-a579-02a4ed507b03/mini__GP11513.jpg?width=1200&height=750" alt="mini__GP11513" class="embeddable-photo__image"/>
            </picture>
        </div>


    </div>
</div><h2>More than goals</h2>
<p>He may be a goalscoring wide forward, but he also provides chances for his teammates. In addition to the 18 goals in 36 games, he has accumulated<strong> 11 assists</strong>. That puts him second for assists in LaLiga for the season, with only teammate Lamine Yamal ahead on 15.</p>
<p>Raphinha has achieved numbers this season to show he is a key player in attack, making him a worthy winner of the best LaLiga player of the season award. There is no denying that the blaugrana number 11 has been one of the sensations of the season.</p></div>


